2024-05-17 14:49:40 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1715957380,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"165.231.35.204","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (X11; Linux i686; rv:114.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/114.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10019,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"7686","cat_id":"3","project_id":"1366","nick":"Emily","content":"Hi there,\r\n\r\nWe run a YouTube growth service, which increases your number of subscribers both safely and practically.\r\n\r\nWe go beyond just subscriber numbers. We focus on attracting viewers genuinely interested in your niche, leading to long-term engagement with your content. Our approach leverages optimization, community building, and content promotion for sustainable growth, not quick fixes. Additionally, a dedicated team analyzes your channel and creates a personalized plan to unlock your full potential, all without relying on bots.\r\n\r\nOur packages start from just $60 (USD) per month.\r\n\r\nWould this be of interest?\r\n\r\nKind Regards,\r\nEmily","create_date":"2024-05-17 14:49:40","modify_date":"2024-05-17 14:49:40","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2564911},"entity_changes":false}
